@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:5072

### Root
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Create Turnstile task
GET {{baseUrl}}/turnstile?url=https://example.com&sitekey=YOUR_SITEKEY

### Poll task result
GET {{baseUrl}}/result?id=REPLACE_TASK_ID

### Missing params example
GET {{baseUrl}}/turnstile

### SUNARP consultar
GET {{baseUrl}}/consultar?url=https://consultavehicular.sunarp.gob.pe/&sitekey=0x4AAAAAACFzt4Xn8T1Jg9ZS&placa=ABC123

### Expected create response
# {
#   "errorId": 0,
#   "taskId": "uuid-here"
# }

### Expected processing response
# {
#   "status": "processing"
# }

### Expected ready response
# {
#   "errorId": 0,
#   "status": "ready",
#   "solution": {
#     "token": "..."
#   }
# }

### Expected error response
# {
#   "errorId": 1,
#   "errorCode": "ERROR_CAPTCHA_UNSOLVABLE",
#   "errorDescription": "Could not solve the Captcha"
# }